# Auth0 Management API credentials
# See: https://auth0.com/docs/api/management/v2/get-access-tokens-for-production
#
# 1. Go to Auth0 Dashboard → Applications → Create Application
# 2. Choose "Machine to Machine Application"
# 3. Authorize it for the "Auth0 Management API"
# 4. Grant these scopes: read:users, create:users, update:users, delete:users, read:roles, create:role_members
# 5. Copy the values below

